<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <style>
            div{
                border-left: 1px solid black;
                padding-top: 1px;
                padding-bottom: 1px;
            }
            h1{
                padding: 5px;
            }
            li{
                padding-left: 30px;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <a href="mgmt.refont">Back to Settings</a>
        <br>
        <br>
        <div id="v1-3">
            <h1>v1.3</h1>
            <li>Finished UX / Settings UI.</li>
            <li>Fixed a bug where update notification did not show in some circumstances.</li>
            <li>Fixed the position of the ReFont logo.</li>
            <li>Prevented text highlighting on browser action.</li>
            <li>Fixed issues where the browserAction did not repond to changes in tabs. This may have solved some performance issues.</li>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div id="v1-2">
            <h1>v1.2</h1>
            <li>New logo.</li>
            <li>Made it easier to tell whether ReFont is enabled by adding a dynamic browser action icon.</li>
            <li>Improved readability on browser action.</li>
            <li>Fixed UX bugs resulting from recent changes.</li>
            <li>Added a changelog.</li>
            <li>Notification on update in browser action with link to changelog.</li>
            <li>Added new 'lists' page to settings.</li>
            <li>Users can now restore the default list.</li>
            <li>The font library and list can be exported to JSON for backup or editing.</li>
            <li>Added a feature which can backup the extension's configuration and restore from the backup.</li>
            <li>Fixed issues where conflicting lists caused the extension to break.</li>
            <li>Pop up message lets users know how many conflicts had to be resloved to import a list.</li>
            <li>Added a feedback button to the settings page.</li>
            <li>Miscellaneous improvements.</li>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div id="v1-1">
            <h1>v1.1</h1>
            <li>User Interface optimisations.</li>
            <li>User Interface bug fixes.</li>
            <li>Miscellaneous improvements.</li>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div id="v1-0-4">
            <h1>v1.0.4</h1>
            <li>Improvements to the browser action user interface for enhanced ease of use.</li>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div id="v1-0-3">
            <h1>v1.0.3</h1>
            <li>Minor edits to UI.</li>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div id="v1-0-2">
            <h1>v1.0.2</h1>
            <li>Minor bug fix.</li>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div id="v1-0-1">
            <h1>v1.0.1</h1>
            <li>Fixed a bug which prevented the user from disabling the font changer.</li>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div id="v1">
            <h1>v1</h1>
            <li>ReFont is released!</li>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>